refsect1.para:
Mandatory arguments to long options are mandatory for short options too.


  &opt_h;
  &opt_help;



      display help message and terminate





  &opt_version;



      display version information and terminate





  &opt_q;
  &opt_quiet;



      do not display warning messages





  &opt_v;
  &opt_verbose;



      display concise intermediate messages





  &opt_d;
  &opt_debug;



      display detailed intermediate messages





  &opt_f;
  &opt_freevar;



      do not replace free variables in the LPS with dummy values





  &opt_y;
  &opt_dummy;



      replace free variables in the LPS with dummy values (default)





  &opt_u;
  &opt_unused-data;



      do not remove unused parts of the data specification





  &opt_c;
  &opt_vector;



      store state in a vector (fastest, default)





  &opt_r;
  &opt_tree;



      store state in a tree (for memory efficiency)





  &opt_R;&name;
  &opt_rewriter;=&name;



       use rewriter &name; (default 'inner')
